QuestData.Description:
Now that you have seen the basics it is time for us to expand your understanding.
I hope your little mind will be able to hold this information.
You seem capable so far, but you are so small. I'll be intrigued to see if you are bigger on the inside.
First. You need to learn more about the catalysts. There should be a small number growing in this very grove. Fetch me some and I can explain what they are.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find some Catalysts in the grove.
